&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Would you like to support your local NHS Trust?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for Bank Staff to work in clinical and non-clinical roles in Solent NHS Trust &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you have any free time, want to earn some extra cash and support your Solent NHS Trust during this busy time then we want to hear from you.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for Bank Healthcare Support Workers to work in our inpatient wards and clinics across Southampton.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Applicants must have experience of working in a care environment as some experience is required to work on our busy wards. A care certificate is desirable for this role however training for this can be offered. We are looking for motivated, enthusiastic individuals who possess good communication skills. You must be able to work flexibly and able to work a mixture of early and late shifts. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role you will be required to provide support to our nursing teams under the supervision of the Lead Nurse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supportive Orientation Period&lt;/strong&gt;: Shadow shifts will be offered prior to working on our wards for training, development and to understand the working of the wards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information about this role please see the job description and to find out the hours and shifts patterns, please contact recruitment@solent.nhs.uk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note we are looking to hold interviews every week on a Monday, Tuesday or Wednesday between 2pm and 4pm to support nurses in the current situation.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
